    "Is the potential for AI-enabled personalised therapeutics being over hyped?",
    "AI approaches, such as those applied in computer vision and natural language models 26, have advanced substantially in the last decade and there is increasing consensus on and evidence for their transformative potential in medicine 7, 19, [27] [28] [29].",
